                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "西风剑术·女仆"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护体岩铠</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/b6fb31387815c4484390c7fb11891609_7319050076591021840.png",
                "id": "talent30642",
                "key": "护心铠",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "护心铠"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大扫除</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/cb9d679d3462bed59d1601663836a019_4121986942710308323.png",
                "id": "talent23958",
                "key": "大扫除",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "大扫除"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（冰）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（水）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（火）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（雷）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_8870695652540133180.png",
                "id": "talent49982",
                "key": "岩元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">护体岩铠</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>为我方出战角色提供<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2点护盾</span>。</p><p>此<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>耗尽前，我方受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>减半。（向上取整）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">大扫除</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>角色使用普通攻击时：少花费1个<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p>角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻击</span>造成的伤害+2，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/26/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5639564980816597000.png",
